Package: SharePointR
Title: Functionality to connect to Microsoft Sharepoint from R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alex", "Weirth", , "weirth@evergreenecon.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a set of functions to connect to Microsoft SharePoint and
    read/write files directly from R. Includes support for CSV files, Excel files,
    and R data files (.RData, .rda). Enables authenticated access to SharePoint
    sites and drives with easy-to-use functions for seamless data exchange with
    SharePoint repositories.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
